      "08ad15dc-44a0-4b62-ad00-fe1909e59a96"],
     " (corresponding to the nonselective measurement ",
     Cell[BoxData[
      RowBox[{
       StyleBox["\[Rho]", "TR"], "\[VeryThinSpace]", "\[RightTeeArrow]", 
